Class HumanServer

  • java.lang.Object
    • cs2030.simulator.HumanServer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Server
    class HumanServer
extends java.lang.Object
implements Server
    The Human Server class keeps track of who is the customer being served (if any) and who is the customer waiting to be served (if any).
